name: Tri Tachyon Branch HQ
desc: A massive fortified compound stands out amongst the skyscrapers, a testament of Tri-Tachyon's wealth and technology, built in mere months, is already shaping and defining the growing corporate district around it. Local industries send representatives near daily to broker deals with the megacorporation, boosting local industrial output for a cut of the profits.

name: Bakery
desc:
Numerous factories and overcomplicated confectionary lines producing 'your' famed pastries
Due to the lack of the original recipe and experience the flavor is degraded to say the least, and the amount spent on additives and artificial sweeteners to mimic the taste of the real thing is comparable to an entire industry.
But hey, the people love it.

name: Dolos Network Center
desc: A sophisticated network, maintaned by Theta type AI core. This network allows for rapid communications between worlds by using quantum mechanics and unique skills exhibited by Theta AI Core.

name: Archimedes SQC
desc: Archimedes Quantum Supercomputer uses experimental quantum processors to compute data at speeds that has never been witnessed before.

name: Charon Facilitiy
desc: Project Charon was combined effort of Tri Tachyon and Ko Combine to achieve immortality via transfering human consciousness to sophisticated AI cores. Unfortunately this process does not transfer, but merely copies mind of the person, killing them in process. Nontheless this facility is capable of producing Theta AI cores, abilities of which far exceed what was considered to be the limits of the technology in the persean sector.
